Solidbank declares 3 - peso cash dividend . Solidbank Corp said on Monday its board had declared a three - peso cash dividend on all issued and outstanding shares totalling 10 , 223 , 055 . The record and payment date for the cash dividend have yet to fixed pending approval by the Central Bank , the bank said . Solidbank paid a five - peso cash dividend in the second quarter of the year and in 1995 its cash dividends totalled 10 pesos per share . - - Manila newsroom ( 632 ) 841 - 8937 
